systematically measure or report on the size of Thai foreign direct investment in developing countries. For its neighbouring countries, Thailand is a major player in terms of the size of investment provided.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "5310f9e3-cf1c-43ad-88cc-beaf403f6afc": {"__data__": {"id_": "5310f9e3-cf1c-43ad-88cc-beaf403f6afc", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/strategic-review-thailands-international-development-cooperation", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Strategic Review of Thailand\u2019s International Development Cooperation", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/strategic-review-thailands-international-development-cooperation", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "655f60af7badf6b32c999bc4020d02d24f9a5093252859e1b7a882ae459707c5"}, "2": {"node_id": "dd9404cb-755c-4b9f-ad4a-34f5798e7ca3", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/strategic-review-thailands-international-development-cooperation", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "26ed26fcb02b9b86b61dfcccd439e0a51bc50b64225784cde77b1a838ebc1428"}}, "hash": "8a64a99d81dc5a89243bdc6052adfc009fb019f165301e757fc27790fd5b0976", "text": "For its neighbouring countries, Thailand is a major player in terms of the size of investment provided. Country Project Implementing Agency 2009 2010 2011 Cambodia Cambodian - Thailand